| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2947 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7af4bc93-ed12-5a34-9d3a-142925a36018"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
